ns, concern for others, but communication difficulty and egocentric. Which is best? Likely C still best.\n\nWe should state reasoning, note uncertainties (lack of teamwork evidence). Possibly ask if any agent has any positive teamwork evidence not captured, but we already asked and got none. So we can finalize.\n\nThus public message: summarize that we have confirmed no explicit teamwork strengths, no reliability statements for A, B, C, D's stress handling none, D's reliability none, etc. Then evaluate and vote for C.\n\nProceed."}
